Birthday cake

Designed a birthday cake for a dino fanatic.

It features three main dinosaurs from the Jurassic Park/World movies:

  • Spinosaurus from Jurassic Park 3;
  • Indominus Rex from Jurassic World 1;
  • Indoraptor from Jurassic World 2.
